Nichelle Nichols inspiring people

00:03:35.700 --> 00:03:38.430
with Star Trek and the
Starship Enterprise.

00:03:38.430 --> 00:03:40.870
And she was the first
African American woman

00:03:40.870 --> 00:03:44.840
to play a leadership role
in the 60's on television

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:47.160
