00:39:47.860 --> 00:39:49.160
Yes sir?

00:39:49.160 --> 00:39:54.130
&gt;&gt; So I want to be one of the
next astronauts to go to Mars.

00:39:54.130 --> 00:39:55.430
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: Okay.

00:39:55.430 --> 00:40:00.250
&gt;&gt; And I have gotten into all
GT classes and such and such.

00:40:00.250 --> 00:40:03.820
And tried my best with
all that I can do.

00:40:03.820 --> 00:40:07.040
What was your motivation?

00:40:07.040 --> 00:40:09.410
What kept you going?

00:40:09.410 --> 00:40:10.960
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: What
kept me going?

00:40:10.960 --> 00:40:14.000
I think. I mean, again
getting back to.

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:16.450
Have you read The Little
Engine That Could?

00:40:16.450 --> 00:40:18.150
&gt;&gt; Yes, as well as Curious George.

00:40:18.150 --> 00:40:21.510
I have been watching those
ever since I was little.

00:40:21.510 --> 00:40:23.020
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: You have
not read Curious George?

00:40:23.020 --> 00:40:25.210
Not yet. I am telling you over.

00:40:25.210 --> 00:40:28.250
There is something called
the joy of repetition.

00:40:28.250 --> 00:40:31.150
When you have heard
it so many times,

00:40:31.150 --> 00:40:33.620
you already believed
that you can do it.

00:40:33.620 --> 00:40:38.370
And my motivation was again
having people that believed in my

00:40:38.370 --> 00:40:40.000
when I did not believe in myself.

00:40:40.000 --> 00:40:42.780
But you have to build
that internal strength

00:40:42.780 --> 00:40:44.970
and character and discipline.

00:40:44.970 --> 00:40:46.270
That if you fail.

00:40:46.270 --> 00:40:48.480
And there is nothing
wrong with failing.

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:50.680
I failed at many things.

00:40:50.680 --> 00:40:52.960
It is not that you fail.

00:40:52.960 --> 00:40:55.190
It is that you pick
yourself up after the failure

00:40:55.190 --> 00:40:56.850
and figure out what was wrong.

00:40:56.850 --> 00:41:00.990
We built rockets that failed many
times before we got one right

00:41:00.990 --> 00:41:02.560
to get to the Moon.

00:41:02.560 --> 00:41:04.200
So keep going.

00:41:04.200 --> 00:41:05.500
Just keep going.

00:41:05.500 --> 00:41:06.800
Just believe.

00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:11.140 position:56%
And find that person that has your
back and wants you to be successful.

00:41:11.140 --> 00:41:15.390
And grab them and say I
want to be on Mars in 20.

00:41:15.390 --> 00:41:16.690
What how old are you?

00:41:16.690 --> 00:41:17.990
&gt;&gt; I am 12.

00:41:17.990 --> 00:41:19.350
So 2030, 2040.

00:41:19.350 --> 00:41:20.650
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: Okay 2040.

00:41:20.650 --> 00:41:22.910
I want to be on Mars in 2040.

00:41:22.910 --> 00:41:25.490
Email Elon Musk [laughter].

00:41:25.490 --> 00:41:28.880
Seriously, Elon Musk on Instagram.

00:41:28.880 --> 00:41:32.730
Say, Elon, hey I want to go to
Mars on the Falcon Heavy baby.

00:41:32.730 --> 00:41:34.530
Come one. Help me.

00:41:34.530 --> 00:41:36.470
Help me. You know.

00:41:36.470 --> 00:41:39.560
I mean reach out to people
that are doing the things

00:41:39.560 --> 00:41:40.910
that you want to do.

00:41:40.910 --> 00:41:42.210
Reach out to me.

00:41:42.210 --> 00:41:43.510
I am on Instagram.

00:41:43.510 --> 00:41:44.810
Leland Melvin.

00:41:44.810 --> 00:41:46.610
You know and we will
have the discussion.

00:41:46.610 --> 00:41:50.810
And if you get to a road block,
we can overcome that road block.

00:41:50.810 --> 00:41:52.320
You can get through it.

00:41:52.320 --> 00:41:53.620
&gt;&gt; Awesome.

00:41:53.620 --> 00:41:54.920
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: I cannot wait
to see you up there [applause].

00:41:54.920 --> 00:41:59.450
We are out.

00:41:59.450 --> 00:42:01.130
Two minutes.

