Okay. Go ahead.

00:42:04.110 --> 00:42:07.640
&gt;&gt; Hi. I really enjoyed
reading the part of your book

00:42:07.640 --> 00:42:08.940
where you were talking

00:42:08.940 --> 00:42:10.440
about Nichelle Nichols
and her work with NASA.

00:42:10.440 --> 00:42:12.370
I had no idea.

00:42:12.370 --> 00:42:15.980
So, I would like to know your
thoughts about women in STEM.

00:42:15.980 --> 00:42:18.740
There is a group of STEM
students right here.

00:42:18.740 --> 00:42:20.040
One of them is my daughter,

00:42:20.040 --> 00:42:22.390
