program in three days.

00:42:22.390 --> 00:42:24.370
My son is about to
start his third year.

00:42:24.370 --> 00:42:27.010 position:56%
So, I just like your thoughts on it.

00:42:27.010 --> 00:42:29.470 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: So women in STEAM,
I think is what you said, right?

00:42:29.470 --> 00:42:32.990
Women in STEAM?

00:42:32.990 --> 00:42:35.950
