00:42:37.700 --> 00:42:39.000
I want you to go to the website.

00:42:39.000 --> 00:42:42.290
Send all your girls to the
website and this is a place

00:42:42.290 --> 00:42:45.390
that showcases women
doing incredible things.

00:42:45.390 --> 00:42:47.900
Peggy Whitson is a Maker woman.

00:42:47.900 --> 00:42:50.610
And they see their
path, their journey.

00:42:50.610 --> 00:42:56.280
I think about Peggy and her
dream was to be an astronaut.

00:42:56.280 --> 00:42:57.580
Not a goal.

00:42:57.580 --> 00:42:58.880
It was a dream.

00:42:58.880 --> 00:43:02.260
And when Sally Ride became
the first female astronaut,

00:43:02.260 --> 00:43:05.190
her dream changed to a goal.

00:43:05.190 --> 00:43:08.660
She applied 13 times.

00:43:08.660 --> 00:43:09.960
She had a medical condition

00:43:09.960 --> 00:43:11.410
where they said you
cannot be an astronaut.

00:43:11.410 --> 00:43:12.900
She did the research
and found out that

00:43:12.900 --> 00:43:15.650
that is not a problem
for me to go to space.

00:43:15.650 --> 00:43:18.080
So 12 times she was denied.

00:43:18.080 --> 00:43:22.630
And tonight she comes home
as the first U.S. person

00:43:22.630 --> 00:43:25.310
to have 650 days in space.

00:43:25.310 --> 00:43:26.680
So, it is the tenacity.

00:43:26.680 --> 00:43:29.710 position:56%
It is the I think I can and believe.

00:43:29.710 --> 00:43:31.970
And I say, ladies you
can do anything

00:43:31.970 --> 00:43:34.610
that these knucklehead guys can do.

00:43:34.610 --> 00:43:36.790
Okay. Seriously.

00:43:36.790 --> 00:43:39.280
And I am a Maker man
that supports women.

00:43:39.280 --> 00:43:42.640
So, it is just so important
that we do that.

00:43:42.640 --> 00:43:45.210 position:56%
And some of my bosses have been some

00:43:45.210 --> 00:43:47.200
