00:44:42.800 --> 00:44:46.280
&gt;&gt; If you were going to teach
one thing to kids like me

00:44:46.280 --> 00:44:51.700
and new young generations of
astronauts, what would it be?

00:44:51.700 --> 00:44:56.140
&gt;&gt; Leland Melvin: The one thing
that I would tell you to do is,

00:44:56.140 --> 00:44:57.870
I think Mark Twain said it.

00:44:57.870 --> 00:45:00.510
The two most important days of
your life are the day you were born

00:45:00.510 --> 00:45:02.450
and the day you figure out why.

00:45:02.450 --> 00:45:07.010
Study, learn, figure out
why you exist on this planet

00:45:07.010 --> 00:45:08.400
and what your purpose is.

00:45:08.400 --> 00:45:11.180
To help other people and
advance our civilization.

00:45:11.180 --> 00:45:14.030
And once you figure
that out, it is fun.

